       lliisstt__ccoommmmoonnss can be used to manually check the contents of
       a  common  database. It outputs every common it finds in a
       given database.  lliisstt__ccoommmmoonnss examines a  database  gener-
       ated with ssccaann__ccoommmmoonnss(1).


